{"tid":1881894,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"二手價崩！海怡兩房失守800萬，麗港城每呎萬二有找！","createTime":"2020-02-15T21:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T16:07:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dcbf4338a851dcb1aff18d3a2208bd94b2e125a6","tid":1881894,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T21:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DuRjA5mYVdkDaygEttovNA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/afa4ba9baa2d0780dfa3969de7c6b4a1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDuRjA5mYVdkDaygEttovNA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fafa4ba9baa2d0780dfa3969de7c6b4a1&h=799720c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島藍籌屋苑難敵新冠肺炎，成交價進一步回落，並重現可承做最高九成按揭的單位。由投資集團持有的鴨脷洲海怡半島兩房收租單位，先後劈價合共90萬元，最終以790萬元售出，樓價創項目接近一年新低。<br />\n<br />\n該屋苑上周曾出現低市價放盤，吸引買家排隊睇樓，雖然最終未錄成交，但反映平盤仍有市場。中原盧鏡豪透露，項目出現單日連錄4宗買賣情況，包括上述2座中層C室，實用面積533方呎。最初開價880萬元，其後降至830萬元，最終再劈40萬元沽出。據悉，除了同盤單位之外，上述投資集團亦持有紅磡黃埔花園及茶果嶺麗港城物業，近期同時減價放售。<br />\n<br />\n盧氏續稱，海怡半島另一個11座低層E室單位，剛亦以970萬元轉手，三房單位做價跌穿千萬元，以實用面積633方呎計算，呎價15,324元。<br />\n<br />\n東堤灣畔累劈220萬<br />\n<br />\n九龍市區盤麗港城本月終錄得首宗成交。美林物業陳松林指出，該項目16座一個極低層單位，實用面積748方呎，屬於套三房改四房間隔，最初叫價980萬元，近日減至932萬元，以890萬元售出，呎價僅約11,898元。較個別銀行估價945萬元，低約6%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，東涌繼續出現劈價盤。中原林溢斌表示，東堤灣畔8座低層H室套三房海景單位，累積減價220萬元，以880萬元獲用家承接，實用呎價10,138元。<br />\n<br />\n盛世年半跌價達24%<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主於二○○二年以約314萬元買入該單位，期內帳面獲利566萬元，升值約1.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n至於新界東的大圍盛世3座南翼中層單位，僅以1,000萬元登記售出，呎價14,535元。比二○一八年中的一個同座較低層同室戶做價，低達24%。"},{"pid":"fd6b8f69741be6c0232f6c04f181b8337af72e18","tid":1881894,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T00:44:59.000Z","msg":"面獲利566萬元，升值約1.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n此POST完"},{"pid":"3cd25ab844e33ffab799fb91c36c79169e9297b6","tid":1881894,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:01:47.000Z","msg":"掃貨撚仲唔出場既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e203737629d97d53c1949931b0980f1c25dbf66","tid":1881894,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:05:29.000Z","msg":"100萬就出手"},{"pid":"481a1156103f2f07ca678ec415f7bd78a8431c1f","tid":1881894,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:07:14.000Z","msg":"繼續繼續"},{"pid":"ee56dfcc651478cb387faf47e70a7007d37303b5","tid":1881894,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"平左好多, 要買了, 再唔買就升返"},{"pid":"5d3fb2a2a716fb7a17a1de94daff763460aa3a6e","tid":1881894,"uid":343712,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fd6b8f69741be6c0232f6c04f181b8337af72e18","tid":1881894,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T00:44:59.000Z","msg":"面獲利566萬元，升值約1.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n此POST完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:22:23.000Z","msg":"就係重有賺先肯減得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家大鑊嘅只係2017或之後買樓𠴱班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無大陸人承接，有排冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81b5bda4305405dba0a4b37499cb8970bdc0600","tid":1881894,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:52:42.000Z","msg":"挽完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0cfe440f730d011e6b832e6fbf110a9b21ec1b","tid":1881894,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:07:26.